🔁 Close the Loop (make it self-improving)

1. Calibrate
	•	compare predictions to reality (micro)
	•	compare renders to expert review / audience (macro)

2. Update
	•	adjust priors (costume, lighting, pacing)
	•	refine Anchor constraints and Wraith ranges

3. Version
	•	keep branches (Git-style IR)
	•	track deltas (what changed, why it improved)

4. Measure
	•	clarity (did people understand?)
	•	fidelity (did experts agree?)
	•	engagement (did it hold attention?)

