⚖️ Guardrails (keep it clean)
	•	Label outputs: restored vs enhanced vs probabilistic reconstruction
	•	Respect invariants: don’t alter core performance/story unless declared
	•	Stay calibrated: never outrun your evidence (no over-rendering)
	•	Rights & consent: licensing for films; clear provenance for reconstructions

